version_description:
-New Login Screen Change.
-New companies added in payment Section .
-Minor bugs fixed.
-Transaction Receipt added in Account Statement.

What's new in NBP Digital:
Explore the latest smart features and enjoy convenience on your finger tips

•Bio metric Login
•Virtual Card Addition
•QR Payments
•Pay to any CNIC via Jazz Cash
•Improve customer experience and bug fixes.

We update the NBP Digital as often as possible to make it faster and more reliable for you.

Following enhancements you will find in the current version:

- 1 Bill Payments (Credit Card Payment/ Voucher Payment / Topups).
- UPI QR Merchant Locator has added.
- Various bug fixes and improvements.

Aitemaad Islamic Account Holders can now register on NBP Digital and enjoy banking 24/7.

NEW FEATURES

- 14-digit NBP Account number for fund transfer (IBT)

- Fund transfer - Conventional to Aitemaad Islamic Account

- Fund transfer - Aitemaad Islamic to Conventional Account

- Fund transfer - Aitemaad Islamic to Aitemaad Islamic Account

- Self-Registration

- Security feature (OTP for Login & Device Binding)

- MPIN for all financial transactions

- MPIN Management

- Add Multiple NBP Accounts

- Generate UPI QR
